title: Vasily Kandinsky Boxed Note Cards
description:
Vasily Kandinsky's artwork is some of the most recognizable in the world. His background includes studies in the fields of fine art and law, and he is credited as one of the first painters to create truly abstract art. Bright and bold, this box of versatile cards depicts five of his most iconic works.
  • Dimensions: 5.5 x 7.5 x 1.5 in.
  • Materials: Large-format glossy 2-piece box. Cards printed on coated paper stock
  • 20 notecards and envelopes, 4 each of 5 images.
